---
import { LogoDemo } from '../../../../packages/demo-components/src/LogoDemo';
import IndividualLayout from '../layouts/IndividualLayout.astro';
const selected = '/class-names';
---

<IndividualLayout title="Welcome to SVG Table" selected={selected}>

	<h1>Fine-level Control</h1>
	<p>SVG Table allows you to add className on the table or cells.(default behavior does not create class attributes to save file size.) </p>
	<p>
		Once you add it, the internal structure will automatically generate class names. (i.e. XX-wrapper, XX-content, ...)
	</p>
	<p>
		You can add your own styles such as animation or themes using the class names.</p>

		<h2>Try to hover over each boxes!</h2>
	<div class="logo-holder">
		<LogoDemo width={640}/>
	</div>

	
</IndividualLayout>

<style is:global>
	.logo-holder {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		height: max-content;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		margin-block: 2rem;
	}
	svg, svg *{
		transition: all 200ms linear;
		cursor: pointer;
	}
	.left-top-empty-wrapper:hover .left-top-empty-content > g {
		transform: scale(1.2);
	}
	.right-top-empty-wrapper:hover .right-top-empty-content > g {
		transform: scale(1.2) rotate(45deg);
	}
	.right-bottom-empty-wrapper:hover .right-bottom-empty-content > g {
		transform: translate(0, -30px);
	}
	.left-bottom-empty-wrapper:hover .left-bottom-empty-content > g:first-child {
		translate: 30px;
	}
	.bottom-fill-wrapper:hover .bottom-fill-content > g {
		transform: translate(0, 30px);
	}
	
	.middle-empty-wrapper:hover .middle-empty-content > g { 
		rotate: 180deg;
	}
	@keyframes color-change {
		0% {
			fill: #cee9d0;
		}
		50% {
			fill: #00ff00;
		}
		100% {
			fill: #cee9d0;
		}
	}

	@keyframes text-pulse {
		0% {
			font-size: 14px;
		}
		50% {
			font-size: 20px;
			fill: white;
		}
		100% {
			font-size: 14px;
		}
	}

	.filled-cell-1-wrapper:hover rect{
		animation: color-change 2s linear infinite;
	}

	.filled-cell-wrapper:hover .filled-cell-content text {
		animation: text-pulse .5s linear infinite;
	}
</style>